  [Excerpt] The provincial government decided to appoint the 
following functionaries on 1 June 1994: 
  Zou Benzhen [6760 2609 4176] was appointed vice chairman of 
the provincial economic and trade committee; Zhang Baorui [1728 
1405 3843] was appointed director of the provincial 
pharmaceutical management bureau; Deng Guohua [6772 0948 5478] 
and Ning Zhongyi [1337 1813 5030] were appointed deputy 
directors of the provincial pharmaceutical management bureau; 
Xuan Zhenfu [1357 2182 1381] was appointed deputy director of 
the provincial tourist bureau; Zhang Yingjie [1728 5391 2638] 
was appointed deputy director of the provincial national defense 
scientific and technological industrial office; Han Naiyi [7281 
0035 5030] was appointed deputy director of the provincial water 
resources department; and Chen Benjin [7115 2609 6855] was 
appointed deputy director of the provincial public security 
department. 
